ss-date=2018-10-17|language=en}}</ref> |Outstanding Less than Weekly | |Alianza Metropolitan |- |2006<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.editorandpublisher.com/news/folded-rumbo-among-winners-of-first-nahp-excellence-awards/|title=Folded ‘Rumbo’ Among Winners Of First NAHP Excellence Awards – Editor & Publisher|website=www.editorandpublisher.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-11-02}}</ref> |Outstanding Less than Weekly |Gold |Alianza Metropolitan |- | |Outstanding Editorial Column |Bronze |Rossana Drumond |}
