{{Infobox comics creator biblio |image = NealAdams11.15.08ByLuigiNovi1.jpg |imagesize = |caption = Adams at the [[Big Apple Con]], November 15, 2008. |name = Neal Adams |actstart = 1962 |actend = current |pub1 = [[DC Comics]] |start1 = 1967 |end1 = Present |pub2 = [[Marvel Comics]] |start2 = 1969 |end2 = Present |pub3 = [[Continuity Comics|Continuity]] |start3 = 1984 |end3 = 1994 |sort = Adams, Neal |creatorcomics = |author = y }}
'''[[Neal Adams]]''' is a comic artist and creator who worked on a large number of comic books and characters, particularly for [[DC Comics]] and [[Marvel Comics]], and even creating his own company, [[Continuity Comics]]
